name: Men's Swimsuit Lovers
tagline: Terms of use for Slack community
body:
Hey guys,

Welcome to the men's swimsuit lovers slack community. I created this community for guys who love speedos, thongs, and other "skimpy" swimwear. If you wish to join the community there are some rules you must agree to.

You must be 18+ to join!

This is an inclusive place all is welcome, gay, straight, bi, etc.

Absolutely no trolling or bullying... please be kind and respectful to each other.

You must have a profile pic.

These terms are subject to change at any given time. Enjoy!

Frank
